dc_description_s: Map shows populated areas, shantytowns, roads, and notable features. Includes glossary, city location map, and boundaries index. "Map information as of 1992." "This sheet falls within NA 38-1, 1501, 1:250,000 and NA 38-02, Y630, 1:100,000." "This map is red-light readable." "Printed by DMAHTC 12-92." "DMA stock no. Y921XLUUQ." "A lane is considered as being a minimum of 2.5 meters in width. Normal railroad gauge is 1.44 meters (4ʹ8.5ʹʹ)." "Caution: This product may not conform to the horizontal accuracy requirements.
